{"itemid":305,"subject":"BUSTED FLUSH Signing","event":"Just a reminder, for all of you in the Albuquerque area... and maybe a few who aren't.  Tomorrow is the big mass signing at Page One, New Mexico's largest independent bookstore.\r\n\r\nI'll be there, pen in hand, to sign copies of BUSTED FLUSH, the latest volume in our new Wild Cards triad from Tor.   Contributors Carrie Vaughn, Ian Tregillis, Caroline Spector, Melinda M. Snodgrass, Walton (Bud) Simons, John Jos. Miller, and Victor Milan will also be on hand.  INSIDE STRAIGHT contributor Daniel Abraham is also supposed to drop by, and you may catch glimpses of some of the other Wild Cards writers as well.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/000167xd/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/000167xd/s320x240\" width=\"157\" height=\"240\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\nPage One should also have stacks of other works by most of the particpating writers on hand, so you will be able to get all kinds of other books autographed as well.  \r\n\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/00036fce/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/00036fce\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/00012p5q/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/00012p5q/s320x240\" width=\"185\" height=\"240\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/000373se/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/000373se/s320x240\" width=\"160\" height=\"240\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/000380w5/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/000380w5/s320x240\" width=\"158\" height=\"240\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\nAnd if the Wild Cards crowd isn't enough, this will be joint event with mystery writer John Maddox Roberts, who will be signing the latest of his SPQR series of detective novels set in the late Roman Republic.\r\n\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/00039t9p/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/00039t9p/s320x240\" width=\"159\" height=\"240\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\nThe event will run from 4pm to 6pm tomorrow (Saturday, March 7) at\r\n\r\nPAGE ONE BOOKSTORE\r\n11018 Montgomery Blvd NE\r\nAlbuquerque, New Mexico\r\n\r\nSee you there!","ditemid":78275,"eventtime":"2009-03-06 17:02:00","props":{"personifi_word_count":204,"taglist":"wild cards","opt_screening":"F","current_moodid":41,"commentalter":1237244161,"revnum":1,"revtime":1236385652},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2009-03-07 00:25:37","anum":195,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html","event_timestamp":1236358920,"reply_count":16,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/81733719/731384","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?replyto=5621187","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5621187#t5621187","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5621187#t5621187","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5621187#t5621187","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"infinite_hiatus","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://infinite-hiatus.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5621187,"talkid":21957,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5621187#t5621187","upictitle":"Tyson: SOIAF","article":"While in a bookstore the other day, staring blankly at the shelves wondering what to buy, I realized I haven't gotten into the Wild Cards series because I didn't know where to start.  Do these books need to be read chronologically or can I just pick any one of them up and go from there?  Sorta a lame excuse, but there you go.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"March 7 2009, 00:46:26 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://infinite-hiatus.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"infinite_hiatus","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"infinite_hiatus","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://infinite-hiatus.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"infinite_hiatus","ctime_ts":1236386786,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/64662223/4091018","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?replyto=5621955","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5621955#t5621955","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5621955#t5621955","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5621955#t5621955","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"misunderstruck","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://misunderstruck.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5621955,"talkid":21960,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5621955#t5621955","above":5621187,"upictitle":"Mr. X: dsimpson","article":"The very first Wild Cards book is a good place to start if you want an introduction to the entire universe.<br /><br />However, the recent relaunch begins with <i>Inside Straight</i>, and you won't do too badly by starting with that. <br /><br />The super quick intro goes like this: On September 15, 1946, the Wild Card virus is released over Manhattan. Of those who contract it, most die, some develop bizarre deformities, and very, very few (1%) get (not necessarily useful) superpowers.  The deformed ones are called Jokers, and those with superpowers are called Aces. ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","below":5622211,"ctime":"March 7 2009, 01:58:38 UTC","parent":5621187,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://misunderstruck.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"misunderstruck","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"misunderstruck","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://misunderstruck.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"misunderstruck","ctime_ts":1236391118,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/81375969/9682409","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?replyto=5622211","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5622211#t5622211","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5622211#t5622211","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5622211#t5622211","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"werthead","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://werthead.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5622211,"talkid":21961,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5622211#t5622211","above":5621955,"upictitle":"werthead: Adam 08","article":"I believe the new books are a 'next generation' kind of thing where reading the old ones is not necessary (and tricky as most of them are not in print at the moment). So with the new books you can just start with INSIDE STRAIGHT.<br /><br />I believe the first, original-era WILD CARDS book is just called WILD CARDS, or WILD CARDS I if you can track it down.<br /><br />I'm hoping the rumoured omnibuses of the old books happens, in which case I'll hang on for them before getting into the series.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"March 7 2009, 02:54:36 UTC","parent":5621187,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://werthead.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"werthead","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"werthead","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://werthead.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"werthead","ctime_ts":1236394476,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/81733719/731384","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?replyto=5622467","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5622467#t5622467","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5622467#t5622467","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5622467#t5622467","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"infinite_hiatus","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://infinite-hiatus.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5622467,"talkid":21962,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/78275.html?thread=5622467#t5622467","above":5622211,"upictitle":"Tyson: SOIAF","article":"Thanks!","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"March 7 2009, 04:34:17 UTC","parent":5622211,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://infinite-hiatus.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype"